  "text": "Several pretreatment processes such as ball mill [CITATION_1] , microwave irradiation [CITATION_2] , sodium hydroxide [CITATION_3] , steam explosion [CITATION_4] , ultrasonic [CITATION_5] , biological [CITATION_6] , ozonation [CITATION_7] have been shown to enhance biodegradability of biomass by promoting the hydrolysis process. Since most available articles are addressed based on pretreatment of lignocellulosic biomass, this chapter is mainly focused towards sludge pretreatment.",
